  <description><![CDATA[<p>Chalet Arktic is one of the most popular ski chalets in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, perched slightly above the resort the chalet benefits from having incredible views of the mountains over the lake to Val Claret, the balcony is a great spot to enjoy your afternoon tea. It is only a short walk, around 150 metres, to the slopes and the Chardonnet ski lift, so you can enjoy quick and easy access onto the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>. Chalet Arktic <span><span class="ui-provider a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">is available to book exclusively as well as room by room.</span></span></p>
<h2>Home comforts</h2>
<p><span>The chalet has a modern design and has all of the home comforts you'll need for a home away from home stay. All seven bedrooms are furnished to a high standard in a contemporary Savoyard style and have en-suite facilities. The </span>open plan dining and living area features a fireplace so it's a great place to sit back and relax at the end of the day skiing. After a day of exploring the wonderful ski area, unwind and relax in the sauna or give your achy ski legs a break in the hot tub in the wellness area which has fabulous mountain views over Tignes.  </p>
<h2>Chalet catering</h2>
<p>Chalet Arktic is on a chalet catering board basis. All meals are prepared for you by your designated chalet hosts who are on hand to make your stay as enjoyable as possible. You can look forward to a cooked breakfast, freshly made afternoon tea and a four course evening meal - you also have unlimited wine, beer and soft drinks during dinner. </p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Excellent location - </strong>Located a short walk away from the centre of Tignes and the ski lifts, Chalet Arktic is close to all the amenities you'll need for a week in the mountains.</p>
<p><strong>Chalet team - </strong>Chalet Arktic is a catered chalet, each day breakfast, afternoon tea and dinner will be provided, plus you don't need to worry about the tidying up. Your hosts are there to make you feel right at home and will be looking after you throughout the week.</p>
<p><strong>Great for groups</strong> - The chalet can host fourteen people between the seven twin bedrooms and is designed for socialising given the open plan dining area and living room, it is the perfect choice for groups of families or friends.</p>
<h3><span>Our chalets are going greener, so our mountains don't</span></h3>
<p><span>In all of our chalets we're giving you more choice, with both meat-free and meat options on offer throughout your stay. This is driven as part of our commitment to reduce our </span><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" target="_blank" title="Sustainability">carbon footprint</a><span>.</span></p>]]></description>
