  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ground Floor</strong></p>
<p>Room 1 - Twin beds and single bed recommended for a child in partially separate sleeping area, shower and WC</p>
<p>Room 2, 3, 4, 5, 6 &amp; 7 - Twin beds, shower and WC</p>
